            "id": "4432004",
            "title": "Oil set for weekly gain, gold overtakes Mag 7 stocks as most crowded trade on Wall Street",
            "description": "<html><body><p>Oil prices climbed to a near two-week high on Thursday on supply concerns, while gold (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XAUUSD:CUR\" title=\"Gold Spot Price\">XAUUSD:CUR</a></span></span>) bumped the 'Magnificent Seven' tech stocks to take the top spot as a crowded trade, according to a BofA survey.</p>\n<p>The United States imposed new sanctions to curb Iranian oil exports, while adding to supply concerns, the Organization of the Petroleum Exporting Countries said on Wednesday it had received updated plans for Iraq, Kazakhstan, and other countries to make further output cuts to compensate for pumping above quotas.</p>\n<p class=\"paywall-full-content\">West Texas Intermediate (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CL1:COM\" title=\"Crude Oil Futures\">CL1:COM</a>) crude futures rose ~1% to $63.08/bbl, Brent crude (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CO1:COM\" title=\"Brent Futures\">CO1:COM</a>) up <span style=\"color: #008000;\">+0.8%</span> to $66.38 - both set for a weekly gain. </p>\n<p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember553\">Inventory data in the US also provided some support. </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ETFs: (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/USO\" title=\"United States Oil Fund, LP ETF\">USO</a></span>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BNO\" title=\"United States Brent Oil Fund, LP\">BNO</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UCO\" title=\"ProShares Trust II - ProShares Ultra Bloomberg Crude Oil\">UCO</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SCO\" title=\"ProShares UltraShort Bloomberg Crude Oil ETF\">SCO</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/USL\" title=\"United States 12 Month Oil Fund, LP\">USL</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DBO\" title=\"Invesco DB Oil ETF\">DBO</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DRIP\" title=\"Direxion Daily S&amp;P Oil &amp; Gas Exp. &amp; Prod. Bear 2x Shares ETF\">DRIP</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GUSH\" title=\"Direxion Daily S&amp;P Oil &amp; Gas Exp. &amp; Prod. Bull 2x Shares ETF\">GUSH</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/USOI\" title=\"UBS AG ETRACS Crude Oil Shares Covered Call ETN\">USOI</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNG\" title=\"The United States Natural Gas ETF, LP\">UNG</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BOIL\" title=\"ProShares Trust II - ProShares Ultra Bloomberg Natural Gas\">BOIL</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KOLD\" title=\"ProShares Trust II - ProShares UltraShort Bloomberg Natural Gas\">KOLD</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNL\" title=\"United States 12 Month Natural Gas Fund, LP\">UNL</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FCG\" title=\"First Trust Natural Gas ETF\">FCG</a>)</p>\n<p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember554\">In other news, China’s apparent openness to talks with the US boosted sentiment in global gas markets. European gas and North Asia LNG prices both recorded strong gains, ANZ Research reported.</p>\n<p class=\"yf-1090901\">Gold prices, meanwhile, pulled back from record highs as the U.S. dollar edged higher. </p>\n<p>According to the latest Bank of America fund managers<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/record-gold-crowded-by-one-mega-player-mike-dolan-2025-04-16/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" survey \"> survey </a> published this week, nearly half of the fund managers surveyed (49%) see long gold, or bets that gold prices will rise, as the most crowded trade in the market right now. This marks the first time in two years that fund managers did not see the Magnificent Seven as Wall Street's most crowded trade, according to the survey.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<figure class=\"regular-img-figure\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img alt=\" \" data-caption=\"\" data-original-src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/59039bcfc768b8287b115a6d8f6a798c.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\" data-source=\"Seeking Alpha\" height=\"312\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/59039bcfc768b8287b115a6d8f6a798c.png?io=getty-c-w900\" width=\"900\"/><figcaption class=\"overlay-title\"><p class=\"item-caption\"><span class=\"item-source\">Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure><p class=\"MsoNormal\">ETFs: (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLD\" title=\"SPDR® Gold Shares ETF\">GLD</a></span>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GDX\" title=\"VanEck Vectors Gold Miners ETF\">GDX</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GDXJ\" title=\"VanEck Vectors Junior Gold Miners ETF\">GDXJ</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IAU\" title=\"iShares Gold Trust ETF\">IAU</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NUGT\" title=\"Direxion Daily Gold Miners Index Bull 2x Shares ETF\">NUGT</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PHYS\" title=\"Sprott Physical Gold Trust\">PHYS</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLDM\" title=\"World Gold Trust - SPDR Gold MiniShares Trust\">GLDM</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AAAU\" title=\"Goldman Sachs Physical Gold ETF\">AAAU</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SGOL\" title=\"Aberdeen Standard Physical Gold Shares ETF\">SGOL</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RING\" title=\"iShares MSCI Global Gold Miners ETF\">RING</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAR\" title=\"GraniteShares Gold Trust\">BAR</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OUNZ\" title=\"VanEck Merk Gold Trust\">OUNZ</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SLV\" title=\"iShares Silver Trust ETF\">SLV</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PSLV\" title=\"Sprott Physical Silver Trust\">PSLV</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIVR\" title=\"Aberdeen Standard Physical Silver Shares ETF\">SIVR</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIL\" title=\"Global X Silver Miners ETF\">SIL</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SILJ\" title=\"ETFMG Prime Junior Silver Miners ETF\">SILJ</a>)</p>\n<p> </p>\n</body></html>",
